caption.p: GEL/essential oil nanofiber diameter distribution and scanning electron microscope photos. ( A) GEL nanofibers; ( B– D) GEL/PO nanofibers with PO ratios of 3%, 6%, and 9%; ( E– G) GEL/CO nanofibers with CO ratios of 3%, 6%, and 9%; ( H– J) GEL/PO/CO nanofibers with PO/CO ratios of 3%, 6%, and 9% ( v/v), respectively. Standard deviation and average diameter are referred to as SD and AD, respectively. Reproduced from [ 262] with the copyright permission from American Chemical Society.
